org.jamsim.ascape.navigator

Class RecordedMicroSimTreeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ascape.runtime.swing.navigator.DefaultTreeBuilder
      • org.jamsim.ascape.navigator.MicroSimTreeBuilder
        • org.jamsim.ascape.navigator.RecordedMicroSimTreeBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.ascape.runtime.swing.navigator.TreeBuilder

    public class RecordedMicroSimTreeBuilder
extends MicroSimTreeBuilder
    TreeBuilder that records nodes created so they can be fetched afterwards.

    NB: Must be a subclass of the recorded TreeBuilder, rather than a wrapper, because created nodes may use the TreeBuilder they are built by, which would bypass the wrapper.
